<subSubSection lastPageId="38" lastPageNumber="39" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="36.[264,1323,1851,1878]" lastBlockId="37.[264,1324,284,510]" lastPageId="37" lastPageNumber="38" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[264,409,1851,1877]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Description</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[426,489,1851,1877]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Male</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[506,569,1852,1877]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Head</emphasis>
. Frontal triangle silver­white tomentose, hair wanting; antenna black; scape with white hair; pedicel with short black hair; first flagellomere evenly tapering from base to acuminate apex; antennal ratio: 
<number box="[846,864,324,350]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" value="7.0">7</number>
: 
<number box="[868,884,324,350]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" value="3.0">3</number>
: 
<number box="[889,923,324,350]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" value="17.0">17</number>
; face white pilose, bare medially; silver­white tomentum opposite antennal base; oral margin pale; proboscis projects beyond oral margin for a distance twice head height; gena white pilose and tomentose; occiput white pilose, white tomentum on lower half, scattered; ocellar tubercle with short black hair.
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/156853/files/figure.png" pageId="37" pageNumber="38" targetBox="[327,1255,636,1719]" targetPageId="37">
<paragraph blockId="37.[264,1324,1744,1872]" pageId="37" pageNumber="38">
